{"tid":1585893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一入連登就「獅鳥」十連發? 請手足們停用一切負面字眼","createTime":"2019-09-21T17:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T00:14:44.000Z","uid":197103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8144e02d9eb5a4118a4f1966fba72c99462112d","tid":1585893,"uid":197103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:47:49.000Z","msg":"一開LIVE就睇到, 成班女仔對住鏡頭大叫「獅鳥! 獅鳥! 獅鳥」<br />\n冇野呀?<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">以武制暴又好, 保護老弱婦儒又好, 守護香港秩序又好<br />\n唔好用任何負面字眼去形容手足當下做緊的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n平時自稱甲由/暴塗, 後生仔同溫層就話明白啫<br />\n仲要食對家口水尾, 幫自己營造負面形象?<br />\n仲拎獅鳥做MEME圖?<br />\n<br />\n人地打9你時都只會話執行公務, 維持秩序, 和平乜乜, <strong>門面功夫係極重要</strong><br />\n「獅鳥」本來就係<strong>名不正言不順</strong><br />\n想問點同外國人SPIN「獅鳥」? <br />\n點同係連儂牆睇圖的中老年人/家長解釋?<br />\n點SPREAD勇武背後的理念?<br />\n獅鳥本來理念就真係「以武制暴」架, 點解唔用?<br />\n「以武制暴」一樣包括主動打9黑社會, 點解唔解釋下?<br />\n點解唔用正面的話語鼓勵更多和理非加入?<br />\n信不堅拳何以直?<br />\n<br />\n望住遊行人數一次次咁減少, 就知道「你我永遠不肯定愛不愛誰」啦<br />\n我地係唔可以自滿架<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">好少出PO sorr for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"175a578bebb980608e854ba853d774c76a3258bf","tid":1585893,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:48:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Jack Griffin</span></span>"},{"pid":"e8f4b79ad8960f98e516993a0a0f8b43bae4630b","tid":1585893,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:50:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遊行人數無一次次咁減少<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"31b87aeb4290c30787fb2b5e2f7f0b517a3fe59a","tid":1585893,"uid":197103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"175a578bebb980608e854ba853d774c76a3258bf","tid":1585893,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-2